DESCRIPTION:$. Dan Brownâs international best-seller comes to life on
  stage in this thrilling\, high-stakes adventure! When the curator of the 
 Louvre is found murdered under mysterious circumstances\, symbologist Robe
 rt Langdon and cryptologist Sophie Neveu are thrust into an investigation 
 that quickly unravels into a deadly conspiracy. As they follow a trail of 
 cryptic puzzles and ancient codes\, they discover a secret that could chan
 ge the course of history. Packed with pulse-pounding suspense and stunning
  visuals\, The Da Vinci Code is an exhilarating journey into the unknown.
