DESCRIPTION:$. The Senior capstone serves as a culmination of the experien
 ces and knowledge that Seniors have gained at IU and IUCD\, focusing on an
  embodied choreographic project. Titled "Visions & Voices" this project ex
 plored critical questions such as: What have you learned over the past fou
 r years about yourself and the world around you? What intrigues you? What 
 message do you want to convey to the world through embodied practice? In t
 his capstone project\, Seniors will delve into their individual visions & 
 voices\, allowing for personal exploration and artistic expression.
